SCHEMA: materials/ag_edge.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.materials.ag_edge
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define deterministic AG connection edges.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record ag_edge
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - edge_id: id
    - from_node_id: id
    - to_node_id: id
    - connection_type_id: id
    - extensions: map
  optional:
    - connection_params: map

INVARIANTS:
- Edge ids are unique.
- from_node_id and to_node_id must reference AG nodes.
